{"tid":481804,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"以下喱首歌係獻畀買咗匯豐嘅一眾巴打","createTime":"2017-11-27T13:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T14:29:03.000Z","uid":62067,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12b13e281919325f742a72c2673bf9d3e5e45083","tid":481804,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"大俠霍元甲(萬里長城永不倒)<br />\n<br />\n    作詞：盧國沾<br />\n    作曲：黎小田<br />\n    演唱：徐小明<br />\n<br />\n    <span style=\"color: green;\">[股價]</span>昏睡百年　國人<span style=\"color: green;\">[即係買咗嘅股民]</span>漸已醒　睜開眼吧　小心看吧<br />\n    那個願臣虜自認　因為畏縮<span style=\"color: green;\">[沽貨]</span>與忍讓<span style=\"color: green;\">[死揸]</span>　人家<span style=\"color: green;\">[700、2318]</span>驕氣日盛<br />\n    開口叫吧　高聲叫吧　這裡是全國皆兵<br />\n    歷來強盜要侵入　最終必送命<br />\n    * 萬里長城<span style=\"color: green;\">[十年前試過]</span>永不倒　千里黃河水滔滔<br />\n    江山秀麗疊彩峰嶺　問我國家那象染病<br />\n    衝開血路　揮手上吧　要致力國家中興<span style=\"color: green;\">[上一百再㣫上二百]</span><br />\n    豈讓國土再遭踐踏 *<br />\n    個個負起使命<br />\n    Repeat *<br />\n    這<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睡獅</span></span>漸已醒<br />\n<br />\n歌詞節錄自<a href=\"https://mojim.com/twy104725x42x14.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmojim.com%2Ftwy104725x42x14.htm&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=078b7f91\" target=\"_blank\">https://mojim.com/twy104725x42x14.htm</a>"},{"pid":"15c5ab47ba0ff2ab9b229ed4998ae8637aec778a","tid":481804,"uid":44031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"好撚柒啊巴打你"},{"pid":"5fa95e24dbf75263b003a58da9a317252694772e","tid":481804,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7127a593a343c2e016d468e7c79205549b4e98","tid":481804,"uid":39127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"}]}